description: This 1971 Westfalia VW Bus is cruising all through the town on a very crucial mission, caffeinating the people of Portland with very tasty top-quality coffee. The cool coffee crew exclusively uses their own bus-made syrups to flavor your favorite cups of joe, all made with organic and locally sourced ingredients. You’re sure to adore their selection of Lattes, Cappuccinos, Mochas, and more, and you’ll be pleased to know that they’ll even deliver straight to your door. So next time you’re in need of a fuel-up, you absolutely must try the brews from The Coffee Bus.
name: The Coffee Bus
